  <?dbhtml filename="scrnsaverproto.html"?>

  <title>scrnsaverproto-&scrnsaverproto-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      This extension defines a protocol to control screensaver features and also
      to query screensaver info on specific windows.
    </para>

